It is very easy to operate Wonderchef Regalia Coffee Grinder. Follow the steps below to get the perfect
ground coffee <br>
Step 1: Add coffee beans to the container <br>
Step 2: Rotate the basket to adjust the texture or ground-size <br>
Step 3: Rotate the knob to adjust no. of cups <br>
Step 4: Enjoy freshly grounded coffee <br>
